# Conclave

Governance Control Plane for Federated Learning.

## Getting Started

### Installation

To run Conclave locally during development, set up the virtual environment and install the package in editable mode:

```bash
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -e .
```

### Usage

Run the CLI:

```bash
conclave
```
